\displaystyle\sum_{n=0}^\infty(2^n+i^n)(z-2i)^n
a_n=2^n+i^n
\sum a_n z^n
R=\frac 12
\lim_{n \to +\infty}\left|\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\right|=\lim_{n \to +\infty}\left|\frac{2+\left(\frac{i}{2}\right)^{n+1}}{1+\frac 12\left(\frac{i}{2}\right)^{n}}\right|=2
|z-2i| < \frac 12
|z-2i| > \frac 12
 \lvert 2^n+i^n\rvert=\sqrt{2^{2n}+1}, 
 \lvert 2^n+i^n\rvert^{1/n}=(2^{2n}+1)^{1/2n}, 
 2<(2^{2n}+1)^{1/2n}<(2^{2n}+2^{2n})^{1/2n}=2\cdot 2^{1/2n}\to 2, 
 r=\frac{1}{2}. 
